<view class="page">
  <view class="header">
    <view class="title-main">每日一汤</view>
    <view class="title-sub">9 体质 × 4 季</view>
  </view>

  <scroll-view class="tizhi-row" scroll-x>
    <view wx:for="{{tizhiList}}" wx:key="key"
      class="tizhi-chip {{selectedTizhi == item.key ? 'tizhi-chip-active' : ''}}"
      data-key="{{item.key}}" bindtap="onSelectTizhi">
      {{item.name}}
    </view>
  </scroll-view>

  <view class="card" wx:if="{{today}}">
    <view class="title-sub">{{today.name}}</view>
    <view class="title-tag">{{today.season}}季 · {{tizhiList[tizhiList.findIndex(t => t.key == selectedTizhi)].name}}</view>
    <view class="text-body" style="margin-top: 24rpx;">{{today.desc}}</view>
  </view>

  <view class="nav-row">
    <view class="btn-ghost" bindtap="onTapPrev">换一汤</view>
    <view class="btn-primary" bindtap="onTapNext">下一款</view>
  </view>

  <view class="compliance-bar">
    ✦ 严守声明: 9 体质仅作参考, 汤品仅为生活陪伴, 滋养而非治疗, 不涉及医疗作用。
  </view>
</view>
